rows.label: tlk4170042103_msg0001
rows.name:
The swelling mountains of
clouds... For whose sake
were they made so high?

rows.label: tlk4170042103_msg0002
rows.name:
I wish to express the ridges
of the Cloud Sea, but it
is quite difficult...

rows.label: tlk4170042103_msg0003
rows.name:
It is a great joy to seek
new expressions... Thank
you for inviting me.
